{"tid":1081311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山頂凌宵閣 男子飛墮50米下身亡","createTime":"2019-03-28T08:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T03:39:13.000Z","uid":3090,"like":205,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"48096dbcd7f9218e9f460c2994454b21d2d38031","tid":1081311,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6ZaMk9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6ZaMk9.png&h=93466a01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmxjEGa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvmxjEGa.png&h=3d4dc5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnwgGUw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnwgGUw.png&h=b7ea32dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KDw4QNR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKDw4QNR.png&h=c4721a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7zmS1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7zmS1c.png&h=3a674add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山頂凌宵閣有人從高處墮下斃命。下午1時49分，一名男子由凌宵閣頂層的觀景台位置，飛墮約50米，跌在公廁對開的梯級，當場頭爆骨折，鮮血四濺，傷重身亡。警方正封鎖現場，調查死者身份及墮下原因。<br />\n<br />\n凌宵閣頂層觀景台，收費52元；觀景台上有約1.5米高的欄杆及玻璃圍欄。凌宵閣屬於香港上海大酒店有限公司所有，集團物業部總監孫漫天稱，從閉路電視所見，事主獨個兒到來，付款登上觀景台。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，事主由袋中拿出摺凳踏腳，爬過玻璃欄杆墮下，初步不排除是自殺，但暫時未清楚死者身份，包括是遊客，還是本地人，要交由警方進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台"},{"pid":"3ad7ee065c591b954ac1da008139e88a14c2e149","tid":1081311,"uid":46842,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"又自殺"},{"pid":"124ad0fd758de328a6fcc64297ecf56025039f33","tid":1081311,"uid":78971,"like":720,"dislike":2,"score":718,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08: